                            <li><strong>Content Pipeline</strong> &mdash; From notes to published content</li>
                            <li><strong>Learning System</strong> &mdash; Structured skill acquisition</li>
                            <li><strong>Project OS</strong> &mdash; Ship projects consistently</li>
                            <li><strong>Reflection Engine</strong> &mdash; Periodic reviews and growth tracking</li>
                            <li><strong>Community Layer</strong> &mdash; Collaborate and learn together</li>
                            <li><strong>AI Integration</strong> &mdash; AI-augmented knowledge workflows</li>
